<p class="heading" align="center">Guild Charter</p>
<p class="heading"><a name="1">General Guild Direction</a> <a class="top" href="#top">[TOP]</a></p>
 <p>Our goal is to be the best. We will not and can not accept second place. As such, we raid frequently, starting at 7pm EST on weeknights, and 2pm EST on  
    weekends.</p>

<p class="heading"><a name="2">Guild Charter</a> <a class="top" href="#top">[TOP]</a></p>
 <p>In order to face the challenges provided in the game of Everquest, players must band together in order to succeed. To this end, the guild is the means to
    facilitate the teamwork necessary to succeed. Fury's Edge is a raiding guild, banded together to tackle the toughest challenges Everquest has to offer,  
	both current and future and to allow its members the oppurtunity to participate in the extraordinary encounters and the extremely difficult tasks that can 
	only be accomplished by the elite.
 <p>Fury's Edge is guided by three principles: Friendship, Respect, and Determination. Each of these things is vital for a successful and thriving guild. 
    Friendship is important because at the bottom of it all, Everquest is about having fun, and being with friends is enjoyable. Respect is a fundamental 
    aspect of our guild, both to our own members, and to the other members of the Morell-Thule community. Determination is necessary to ensure that we meet our goals.</p>
<p>Fury's Edge is the combination of two previous rivals with the desire to bring together the best players on Morell-Thule.</p>

